channel.title: !How to fix your compiler!
channel.description:
OK. first off i dont know if this is already posted, im reposting it anyways.
This is just an easy tut on how to fix your compiler, if somone tells me how to add pics, ill add im a forum newb...
FIRST: Go get a working compiler. SECOND: Right click it and click Edit. THIRD: Copy and paste everything in THAT EXACT notepad. FOURTH: Go to your broken compiler. FIFTH: Delete everything in THAT EXACT notepad. SIXTH: !PASTE! what you copied in the working compiler notepad. TADA: Your compiler works! and u may !compile!
(IF) you dont have jdk, thats a way different story. LOLZ!
~WAFFLE-
